data.description: ACTIVE GOLF MEMBERSHIP - Welcome to a professionally furnished and meticulously maintained luxurious oasis serving as your vacation  home, permanent resort living residence or a money-making opportunity as a rental property. This delightful  slice of paradise will not disappoint! Create cherished memories for your family, friends and guests which  will endure a lifetime. Once you step through the door, you'll be captivated by the meticulous upgrades and  attention to detail.  This Reunion Resort home comes fully furnished with top-of-the-line, durable furniture, and cutting-edge  electronics. What's even more enticing is that it includes an active transferable Reunion membership, which  translates to substantial savings of over $10,000! Reunion no longer sells this coveted membership but  honors existing ones. The memberships enable access to the on-site water park, several gyms, pools, hot  tubs, and unlimited golfing! This gem of a house boasts a gorgeous courtyard floorplan, which is a rarity.  Upon entering your oasis, you'll find yourself in a spectacular pool courtyard area. The home boasts not  one, not two, but FOUR balconies/patios, which will overwhelm you with breathtaking views. This home  offers ample space for everyone, beginning with a one-bedroom, one-bathroom apartment above the  garage, complete with its own kitchenette and living room.  A stroll across the second-floor balcony takes you to the main house, where you'll discover two elegant and  luxurious owners' retreats, ideal for multi-generational family travel and comfort. With an abundance of  patios and balconies, two of them overlook the picturesque golf fairway.  This stunning residence spans 2,765 square feet, promising fun, relaxation, and excitement. It features five  bedrooms and four and a half bathrooms, along with an oversized heated pool and spa/hot tub. The home is  fully air-conditioned and has a beautiful Courtyard-style layout, comprising the main house and an annex,  with the courtyard and pool as the focal point. It's perfect as an in-law apartment, and perfect for multiple  families and to offer teenagers and tweens their own "house" for added independence.  The open-plan dining and kitchen space is an inviting hub for family gatherings, cooking, and communal  dining. The kitchen is both modern and well-appointed, showcasing granite countertops and high-end  appliances. French doors on both levels lead to patios with stunning golf course views, providing ample  outdoor space for entertainment or peaceful moments with a great book.  This extraordinary property is situated in the world-class Reunion Resort, a mere six miles from Walt Disney  World® Resort. The resort includes luxurious amenities, including a multi-million-dollar water park. The list  of amenities is extensive; please refer to the photos for a comprehensive description.  Don't miss the opportunity to schedule your private tour before this exceptional property is quickly snapped  up. Recent updates include a new roof in 2022, new carpeting in the main home in 2022, a new A/C system  in 2018, a newer pool/spa heater from 2018, all kitchen appliances added in 2022, and all furnishings added  in 2022. It's all about new, new, new! This house won’t last long on the market!
